OL,6,FFormer Liverpool and Scotland defender
OL,7,FAlan Hansen is seriously ill in
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,FThe club is providing support to the
OL,11,Ffamily of the 68-year-old, who retired
OL,12,Fin 1991 to start a successful career
OL,13,Fas a television pundit.
OL,15,F"The thoughts and support of everyone
OL,16,Fat Liverpool FC are with our legendary
OL,17,Fformer captain Alan Hansen, who is
OL,18,Fcurrently seriously ill in hospital,"
OL,19,Fsaid a Liverpool statement.
