OL,3,CScotland and Liverpool great Alan
OL,4,CHansen seriously ill in hospital
OL,6,F"The club is currently in contact with
OL,7,FAlan's family to provide our support
OL,8,Fat this difficult time, and our
OL,9,Fthoughts, wishes and hopes are with
OL,10,FAlan and all of the Hansen family.
OL,12,F"We will provide any further updates
OL,13,Fas we receive them in due course, and
OL,14,Fwe request that the Hansen family's
OL,15,Fprivacy is respected at this time."
OL,17,FHansen joined Liverpool from Partick
OL,18,FThistle in 1977 and won three European
OL,19,FCups, eight league titles, two FA Cups
OL,20,Fand three League Cups in 620
OL,21,Fappearances for the Anfield side.
